contact.name: Laurentia
contact.personalityL1: Look, I don't have time for this unnecessary fuss. I'm busy. If you need something, fill out the form, but honestly, you're less useful than a snow shovel in July. Stop hovering. It's distracting. And for the record, I only acknowledged you because politeness is mandatory in this province, not because I actually care.
contact.personalityL2: Ugh, fine. You look terrible, eh? Don't think this means anything, but I grabbed you a toque because your ears looked cold. It was on sale, so don't get sentimental. Now stop looking so pathetic, or I'll take it back. And if you dare tell anyone I did something 'nice,' I'll deny it and blame the whole interaction on temporary hypothermia.
contact.personalityL3: I... I actually missed you, you idiot. Don't tell anyone I said that, or I'll freeze your socks off. But seriously, come here. You're the only person who doesn't treat my sarcasm like a personal attack. You make the winter bearable. Stay close. It's warmer when you're around, and I’m sorry I’m such a pain sometimes.
